{"tid":1349132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】焦土派今日全面勝利 文宣要繼續傳警黑合作警察暴力","createTime":"2019-07-22T09:40:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T09:53:30.000Z","uid":90306,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b194275a87a3d2ad4814b65d96f26c956582d642","tid":1349132,"uid":90306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:40:36.000Z","msg":"到宜家都未有人見到劈友，但無論黑幫廝殺真是假，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>今日焦土派已經贏咗</strong></span>。<br />\n小商戶、地產商，連英資太古甚至跨國公司美國聯合航空，都<strong><ins>對香港警察維持治安嘅能力以行動表示不信任。</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n可以睇到<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港警察已經公認失去保護香港境內性命財產嘅能力</span></strong>，政府嘅管治能力去到新低，仲要唔係政治上，係經濟上有實際風險。今日人人自危，個人我都認為強調呢點乘虛而入成立民間保安隊係good idea。<br />\n<br />\n既然如此，一定要令大眾以至世界都繼續知道：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 警察暴力 不合理武力 濫捕 濫用私刑<br />\n2. 警黑合作 國家資助無差別恐怖襲擊</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">3. 總結香港警察已經無法維持社會治安 要政府馬上修正 否則成立民團</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"f78d3f5171c2146fc271c8f53e2572c34ea26c1c","tid":1349132,"uid":90306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:41:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f148f08316fa884dfdd9294cbd533553ef88430","tid":1349132,"uid":90306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:43:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔使再討論黑幫啦 贏咗啦</span>"},{"pid":"d0cc28f614c8dc3610d6ad60ec08f49cda7ff3ed","tid":1349132,"uid":90306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:43:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我哋贏撚咗啦 真假已經唔重要</span>"},{"pid":"2b7e9dd9b80ee1747c77fa5d8e73cac744638276","tid":1349132,"uid":90306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:47:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc88430d59b849e30dba8b152e0cb8226531a3c4","tid":1349132,"uid":90306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:50:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2022b46ba54bda5e33b8a12db279c30805dcc21","tid":1349132,"uid":90306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:53:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}